testcase.name: Automation

failure.message:

Expected contrast ratio of 4.5:1
b) [".dropdown-toggle"] Fix any of the following: Element has insufficient color contrast of 1.94 (foreground color: #777777, background color: #4a4b4d, font size: 11.3pt, font weight: bold). Expected contrast ratio of 4.5:1
c) ["a[href$=\"around.php\"]"] Fix any of the following: Element has insufficient color contrast of 1.94 (foreground color: #777777, background color: #4a4b4d, font size: 11.3pt, font weight: bold). Expected contrast ratio of 4.5:1
d) ["a[href$=\"team.php\"]"] Fix any of the following: Element has insufficient color contrast of 1.94 (foreground color: #777777, background color: #4a4b4d, font size: 11.3pt, font weight: bold). Expected contrast ratio of 4.5:1
e) ["a[href$=\"contact.php\"]"] Fix any of the following: Element has insufficient color contrast of 1.94 (foreground color: #777777, background color: #4a4b4d, font size: 11.3pt, font weight: bold). Expected contrast ratio of 4.5:1
f) ["a[href$=\"booking.php\"] > b"] Fix any of the following: Element has insufficient color contrast of 2.18 (foreground color: #ff0000, background color: #4a4b4d, font size: 17.3pt, font weight: bold). Expected contrast ratio of 3:1
g) ["li > a[href$=\"date.php\"]"] Fix any of the following: Element has insufficient color contrast of 1.94 (foreground color: #777777, background color: #4a4b4d, font size: 11.3pt, font weight: bold). Expected contrast ratio of 4.5:1
h) [".close"] Fix any of the following: Element has insufficient color contrast of 1.6 (foreground color: #cccccc, background color: #ffffff, font size: 15.8pt, font weight: bold). Expected contrast ratio of 3:1
i) ["p:nth-child(2) > b"] Fix any of the following: Element has insufficient color contrast of 3.82 (foreground color: #ff0000, background color: #f8faff, font size: 11.3pt, font weight: bold). Expected contrast ratio of 4.5:1
2) id attribute value must be unique: https://dequeuniversity.com/rules/axe/3.1/duplicate-id?application=axeAPI a) [".collapse"] Fix any of the following: Document has multiple static elements with the same id attribute

4) Page must have one main landmark: https://dequeuniversity.com/rules/axe/3.1/landmark-one-main?application=axeAPI a) ["html"] Fix all of the following: Page does not have a main landmark
5) Links must have discernible text: https://dequeuniversity.com/rules/axe/3.1/link-name?application=axeAPI a) ["a[href$=\"kas_pathar_trek.php\"]"] Fix all of the following: Element is in tab order and does not have accessible text
Fix any of the following: Element does not have text that is visible to screen readers aria-label attribute does not exist or is empty aria-labelledby attribute does not exist, references elements that do not exist or references elements that are empty Element's default semantics were not overridden with role="presentation" Element's default semantics were not overridden with role="none"
b) [".left"] Fix all of the following: Element is in tab order and does not have accessible text

c) [".right"] Fix all of the following: Element is in tab order and does not have accessible text
Fix any of the following: Element does not have text that is visible to screen readers aria-label attribute does not exist or is empty aria-labelledby attribute does not exist, references elements that do not exist or references elements that are empty Element's default semantics were not overridden with role="presentation" Element's default semantics were not overridden with role="none"
6) <marquee> elements are deprecated and must not be used: https://dequeuniversity.com/rules/axe/3.1/marquee?application=axeAPI a) ["marquee:nth-child(1)"] Fix all of the following: Element is visible
b) ["marquee:nth-child(3)"] Fix all of the following: Element is visible
7) Page must contain a level-one heading: https://dequeuniversity.com/rules/axe/3.1/page-has-heading-one?application=axeAPI a) ["html"] Fix all of the following: Page must have a level-one heading
